            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1299677</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>東風風行香港總代理東騰車業正式發佈全新右軚版本純電 SUV「Forthing Friday」（風行 05）登陸香港，標誌該品牌加速邁向全面電動化之路的重要一步。新車融合年輕化設計與前沿智能科技，並以港幣 HK$218,000 的一換一意向價進軍本地市場，冀能吸引尋求實用與個性兼備的電動車買家。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299692" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250327_110403-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250327_110403-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250327_110403.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299682" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250327_105915-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250327_105915-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250327_105915.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>東風柳汽旗下的「風行」品牌近年積極推動新能源轉型，風行 05 為品牌「光合未來」計劃的首個重要成果。官方表示，品牌正計劃於未來 3 年全面電動化、5 年內全面停產燃油車，並期望 2030 年實現碳達峯、2060 年達至碳中和。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299691" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250327_112149-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250327_112149-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250327_112149.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299695" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250327_105938-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250327_105938-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250327_105938.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299696" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250327_105925-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250327_105925-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250327_105925.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>風行 05 外形設計以「曠野電動馳騁」為主題，車頭採用封閉式進氣格柵及蜂窩裝飾面板，搭配分體式 LED 頭燈，營造出強烈科技感。車尾配備貫穿式天際線 LED 尾燈，視覺效果鮮明突出。車身尺寸為 4600mm × 1860mm × 1680mm，軸距達 2715mm，結合短懸長軸設計，空間感與靈活度兼具。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299690" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250327_112310-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250327_112310-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250327_112310.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299687" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250327_112401-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250327_112401-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250327_112401.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299688" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250327_112347-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250327_112347-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250327_112347.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>動力方面，前輪驅動的風行 05 搭載由 BYD 弗迪動力提供的 150kW 永磁同步電機，最大馬力 201 匹，峯值扭力達 340Nm，0 至 100km/h 加速需時 7.9 秒。配合 64.4kWh 鎧甲電池提供高達 500 公里 CLTC 續航力，並支援 35 分鐘由 0% 快充至 80%，應付城市及長途駕駛均遊刃有餘。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299689" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250327_112337-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250327_112337-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250327_112337.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299693" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250327_110310-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250327_110310-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250327_110310.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299694" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250327_110305-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250327_110305-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250327_110305.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>車箱配置方面，風行 05 採用對稱式中控台配搭圓形出風口，塑造年輕與現代感氛圍。主駕座位設有電動按摩座椅連冷凳功能、雙聯屏智慧座艙、同時支援 Apple CarPlay 及 Android Auto。隨車配備 480 公升尾箱與多個收納位，對家庭出行需求提供全面支援。新車配備 FX-Drive 智能駕駛系統，支援 L2+ 級輔助駕駛功能，包括前方碰撞預警、車道保持、360 度全景影像及智能限速提醒等共 12 項主動安全功能，加上泊車雷達與 ABS、EBS 制動系統，為用户提供更全面駕駛保障。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299685" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250327_112528-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250327_112528-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250327_112528.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>規格表:</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-1299681 alignleft" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/05.png" alt="" width="675" height="410" /></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
