        <item>
            <title>Samsung 聯乘 Art Basel 引領藝術新視界，展示全新「The Frame Pro」藝術電視系列</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/27/samsung-art-basel/wireless-home/audio-visual/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=samsung-art-basel</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/27/samsung-art-basel/wireless-home/audio-visual/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 27 Mar 2025 11:30:08 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[家居無線]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[影音產品]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1299757</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p class="" data-start="79" data-end="326">Samsung 與國際級藝術盛事 Art Basel 展開全球合作，成為今年四地展會（包括香港、瑞士巴塞爾、巴黎及美國邁阿密海灘）的官方藝術展示電視品牌。這次聯乘也見證 Samsung 推出「2025 全新 Art TV 系列」的全球首展。今日 Samsung 率先於香港會議展覽中心亮相的 ArtCube 展區，由升級版畫框電視 The Frame Pro、Micro LED、Neo QLED 8K 及 QLED 構建沉浸式藝術空間，展現如何透過創新技術，讓藝術走入日常生活。</p><p class="" data-start="328" data-end="448">Samsung 香港區董事總經理趙依音表示，今次合作有助推動當代藝術普及化，亦讓品牌與 Art Basel 的國際藝廊與藝術家建立長遠夥伴關係。「2025 全新 Art TV 系列」希望將藝術欣賞體驗由展場延伸至家中，打破地域與形式的限制。</p><p data-start="328" data-end="448"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dji_20250327151958_0.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1299768 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dji_20250327151958_0-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dji_20250327151958_0-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dji_20250327151958_0.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2 data-start="450" data-end="480">Samsung Art Store 推動全球藝術串流平台</h2><p class="" data-start="482" data-end="678">Samsung 除了以最新電視硬件提升視覺效果，亦積極透過 Samsung Art Store 將世界級藝術帶進千家萬户。由即日起，用户可以在 Art TV 系列的畫面上，串流欣賞來自 Art Basel 香港展會精選的 23 幅藝廊作品。這些作品將於 3 月 26 日至 30 日期間於會展現場展出，同時也能透過 Art Store 以 4K 解像度在家觀賞，感受藝術原作的色彩層次與細節。</p><p data-start="482" data-end="678"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/samsungarttvatartbas-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299762" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/samsungarttvatartbas-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/samsungarttvatartbas-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/samsungarttvatartbas-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p data-start="482" data-end="678"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/samsungarttvatartbas-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299763" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/samsungarttvatartbas-1-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/samsungarttvatartbas-1-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/samsungarttvatartbas-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p class="" data-start="680" data-end="833">Samsung 自 2017 年推出 The Frame 畫框電視後，至今已與超過 70 間國際博物館及藝廊，包括 MoMA、羅浮宮及梵高博物館合作，累積超過 3,000 件藝術作品供訂閲欣賞。今年起，這些藝術資源將支援 MICRO LED、Neo QLED 及 QLED 系列電視，擴展至更廣泛用户層面。</p><p data-start="680" data-end="833"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/samsungartstore.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299764" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/samsungartstore-694x382.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="382" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/samsungartstore-694x382.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/samsungartstore.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p data-start="680" data-end="833"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/artistmarcdennis.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299765" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/artistmarcdennis-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/artistmarcdennis-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/artistmarcdennis.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2 data-start="835" data-end="855">ArtCube 展區帶來互動藝術體驗</h2><p class="" data-start="857" data-end="1085">今年 Art Basel 香港展會新增名為「ArtCube」的互動展區，選址於香港會議展覽中心 L3 層大堂。展覽主題為「Borderless, Dive into the Art」，由五位國際藝術家（Lee Kunyong、Aerosyn-Lex Mestrovic、Saya Woolfalk、Marc Dennis 及 Jules de Balincount）聯同參展藝廊攜手策展，觀眾可透過 2025 年系列電視沉浸式體驗結合科技與藝術的創作魅力。</p><p class="" data-start="1087" data-end="1105">ArtCube 於以下時間對外開放：</p><ul data-start="1106" data-end="1193"><li class="" data-start="1106" data-end="1134"><p class="" data-start="1108" data-end="1134">3 月 28 日（星期五）下午 2 時至晚上 8 時</p></li><li class="" data-start="1135" data-end="1163"><p class="" data-start="1137" data-end="1163">3 月 29 日（星期六）下午 2 時至晚上 8 時</p></li><li class="" data-start="1164" data-end="1193"><p class="" data-start="1166" data-end="1193">3 月 30 日（星期日）中午 12 時至下午 6 時</p></li></ul><h2 data-start="1195" data-end="1226"></h2><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dji_20250327152712_0.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1299772 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dji_20250327152712_0-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dji_20250327152712_0-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dji_20250327152712_0.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/yiyinzhaomanagingdir.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299766" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/yiyinzhaomanagingdir-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/yiyinzhaomanagingdir-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/yiyinzhaomanagingdir.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dji_20250327152113_0.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1299770 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dji_20250327152113_0-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dji_20250327152113_0-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dji_20250327152113_0.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dji_20250327152020_0.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1299774" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dji_20250327152020_0-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dji_20250327152020_0-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dji_20250327152020_0.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dji_20250327151956_0.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1299775" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dji_20250327151956_0-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dji_20250327151956_0-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dji_20250327151956_0.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dji_20250327151953_0.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1299776" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dji_20250327151953_0-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dji_20250327151953_0-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dji_20250327151953_0.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2 data-start="1195" data-end="1226">The Frame Pro 首度亮相，無線連接擴展家居美學</h2><p class="" data-start="1228" data-end="1374">全新 The Frame Pro 畫框電視於今次展會首次公開亮相，推出支援 4K 144Hz 無線影音傳輸的 Wireless One Connect 技術，有效傳輸範圍達 10 米，擺放方式更靈活，打破傳統空間限制。畫質方面，升級至 Neo QLED 顯示技術，還原藝術作品真實色彩與細節。</p><p data-start="1228" data-end="1374"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05405.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299780" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05405-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05405-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05405.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p data-start="1228" data-end="1374"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05409.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299777" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05409-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05409-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05409.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p data-start="1228" data-end="1374"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05410.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299778" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05410-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05410-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05410.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p data-start="1228" data-end="1374"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05411.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299779" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05411-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05411-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05411.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p class="" data-start="1376" data-end="1516">除了硬件提升，The Frame Pro 每月提供超過 370 件免費藝術品串流，並內置 Samsung Art Store，收藏全球著名藝術館如 MoMA、羅浮宮的作品，亦獨家加入 Art Basel 精選藝術品。該系列亦獲得色彩權威機構 PANTONE 認證，保證畫面還原度。</p><p class="" data-start="1518" data-end="1604">香港 Samsung 網上商店現正接受預訂，凡於 3 月 27 日至 4 月 13 日期間訂購，將獲一年 Art Store 免費訂閲及電視邊框一套（數量有限，先到先得）。</p><p data-start="1518" data-end="1604"><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/03/27/samsung-art-basel/wireless-home/audio-visual/">Samsung 聯乘 Art Basel 引領藝術新視界，展示全新「The Frame Pro」藝術電視系列</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
